title: Ep. 210 Andrew Horowitz: Why Stocks Won't Pullback
itunes:title: Andrew Horowitz: Why Stocks Won't Pullback
description: This week, Andrew Horowitz, President and founder of Horowitz and Co. joins S&A Investor Radio and explains why the Federal Reserve will Keep a floor under the stock market.
